translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「うちら、ここに全員揃ってる……
「アア？　気づいてなかったのか？
そういえば元就がいない！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Now that you mention it, Motonari isn't here!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「闘神都市に来た途端に騒ぎを起こしてね、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "As soon as he came to the Battle God City, he caused a commotion,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 街の刑務所にブチ込まれたよ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: they threw him into the city's prison."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 今日からこの部屋のボスは
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: From today onward, you are the boss of this room—

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あなた様でございますー！」
「ぐわーーっはっはっはっはっ！
牢屋の全員、あなた様に締められたわけで、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Everyone in the cell is under your command,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: もう逆らう気なんて、とてもとても！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and none of us would ever think of defying you!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 元就は牢屋内にいる囚人達に、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Motonari was bowed to by the prisoners inside the cell.
They had their heads lowered to him.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: もう何度も言ったように、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I've told you several times already,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 闘神都市の刑務所の中でして」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: this is the prison inside Battle God City."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「何故、オレはそんなところにいる！？」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Why the hell am I in a place like this!?"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ま、あいつはあいつで今頃楽しくやってるだろ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Well, he's probably having fun on his own by now."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あいつ出すとうっせーから、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "If we let him out, he'll be noisy,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 絶対に出そうとすんじゃねーぞ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: so don't you dare try to get him out."
and we'll pick him up when it's time to go back."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「二人とも男兄弟には結構厳しいね……」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "You two are pretty tough on your brothers..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ま、俺らは闘神大会に集中すっか」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Well, let's focus on the Battle God Tournament."
"Ah, speaking of the Battle God Tournament..."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「ドギの奴も今日が試合だったらしいぜ」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "It seems that Dogi had a match today too."

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「あいつが本当に強くなってたら……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "If that guy really has gotten stronger...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 「闘神ダイジェスト！　確認してみようぜ！」
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: "Battle God Digest! Let's check it out!"

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 長田君が魔法ビジョンのスイッチを入れると、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: When Nagata switched on the magic vision,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 室内にいた皆も注目を始めた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: everyone in the room started paying attention.
